#03.4 create subset for each source
filtered_ARWU=filtered_df[filtered_df['source']==('ARWU')]
filtered_CWU=filtered_df[filtered_df['source']==('CWU')]
filtered_THE=filtered_df[filtered_df['source']==('THE')]
In [36]:
#03.4 create column subset
sub_ARWU=filtered_ARWU[['world_rank', 'total_score', 'ARWU_alumni_prizes', 'ARWU_awards', 'ARWU_highly_cited', 'ARWU_papers_published', 'ARWU_papers_indexed']]
sub_CWU=filtered_CWU[['world_rank', 'total_score', 'CWU_quality_education', 'CWU_alumni_employment', 'CWU_quality_of_faculty', 'CWU_publications', 'CWU_influence', 'CWU_citations', 'CWU_broad_impact', 'CWU_patents']]
sub_THE=filtered_THE[['world_rank', 'total_score', 'THE_teaching', 'THE_international', 'THE_research', 'THE_citations', 'THE_income']]

04 Correlation Matrix

In [39]:
#04.1 create correlation matrix
correlation_matrix_ARWU = sub_ARWU.corr()
correlation_matrix_CWU = sub_CWU.corr()
correlation_matrix_THE = sub_THE.corr()
In [41]:
#04.2 create heatmap
plt.figure(figsize=(10, 10))
sns.heatmap(correlation_matrix_ARWU, vmin=-1, vmax=1, annot = True, cmap = 'PRGn', fmt ='.3f', linewidths=.5)
plt.title('Correlation Heatmap')

plt.figure(figsize=(10, 10))
sns.heatmap(correlation_matrix_CWU, vmin=-1, vmax=1, annot = True, cmap = 'PRGn', fmt ='.3f', linewidths=.5)
plt.title('Correlation Heatmap')

plt.figure(figsize=(10, 10))
sns.heatmap(correlation_matrix_THE, vmin=-1, vmax=1, annot = True, cmap = 'PRGn', fmt ='.3f', linewidths=.5)
plt.title('Correlation Heatmap')
Out[41]:
Text(0.5, 1.0, 'Correlation Heatmap')

49.999082263433195
In [69]:
#07.4 create high category
df.loc[df['total_score'] >= 65, 'Score Category'] = 'High Score'
In [71]:
#09.5 create middle category
df.loc[(df['total_score'] >= 35) & (df['total_score'] < 65), 'Score Category'] = 'Middle Score'
In [73]:
#07.6 create low category
df.loc[df['total_score'] < 35, 'Score Category'] = 'Low Score'
